# Trivia Quiz

A modular and scalable **Trivia Quiz web application** built using  
**HTML, CSS, and modern JavaScript (ES Modules).**

Originally started as a beginner learning exercise inspired by a quiz concept seen in the **Mimo learning platform**, this project has evolved into a structured frontend application focused on:

- modular application architecture
- state management
- UI rendering flow control
- scalable quiz generation logic
- maintainable CSS structure
- refactoring and debugging workflows

The project demonstrates how to build a **real browser application without frameworks**, while still applying professional frontend engineering principles.

---

# Live Demo

https://blackravenwolf.github.io/trivia-quiz/

---

# Purpose

This project serves as an **advanced frontend learning and portfolio project**.

Main learning goals:

- Building a real modular JavaScript application
- Managing application state without frameworks
- Designing scalable UI rendering logic
- Structuring large frontend projects professionally
- Practicing debugging and refactoring techniques
- Preparing architecture for future multiplayer and backend integration

---

# Features

## Gameplay

- Large categorized question database
- Difficulty levels: Easy / Medium / Hard / Expert
- Mixed difficulty distribution logic
- Randomized question selection per session
- No duplicate questions within a quiz
- Shuffled answer options
- Automatic answer validation after selection
- Countdown timer per question
- Real-time score tracking
- Animated progress bar

## Screens

- Start screen
- Options screen
- Credits screen
- Quiz gameplay screen
- Final completion state
- Restart quiz functionality
- Return to main menu

## Quiz Settings

- Difficulty selection
- Question amount selection (Quick в†’ Ultimate)
- Multi-category filtering
- Live preview of selected settings

## UI / UX

- Glassmorphism quiz container
- Gradient background overlay
- Window-style header bar
- Animated timer and score indicators
- Smooth feedback transitions
- Fully responsive layout (desktop / tablet / mobile)

